=== CHILD_STOWAWAY ===
# id: 49
# title: The Child Stowaway
# chinese_title: 偷渡儿童
# category: Crew
# mode: dungeon

A small face peers at you from behind a cargo container — a child, maybe ten years old, clutching a worn stuffed animal. They've been hiding here since the station went dark, surviving on stolen rations. They look at you with a mix of fear and hope.

* [Take the child under your protection]
  ~ gain_radical("子")
  "子" (zǐ) — child, young one
* [Give them food and mark the spot as safe]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "守" (shǒu) — to guard, to protect
* [Ask the child what they've seen]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "说" (shuō) — to speak, to tell
* [Contact authorities for rescue]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "呼" (hū) — to call out
